{"tid":455381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊威利將成大陸人 中國將拍《銀河英雄傳說》真人電影","createTime":"2017-11-02T04:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T17:11:13.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a13bf8e2a4e70f4c51a7f56d2893a29093cb6714","tid":455381,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"日本小說家田中芳樹的科幻巨作《銀河英雄傳說》（簡稱銀英傳），曾多次改編為漫畫、動畫、舞台劇、遊戲，將首次拍成真人版電影，但叫人跌破眼鏡的是由中國稼軒環球影業公司拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n《銀英傳》背景設定為遙遠未來的浩瀚宇宙中，專制君主制的「銀河帝國」與民主共和制的「自由行星同盟」長年打仗，加上夾在中間的強大經濟體「獨立城邦國家費沙自治領」，三方勢力錯綜複雜的交鋒。<br />\n真人版電影《銀英傳》預計拍三部曲，首集於2020年推出；負責拍攝的中國稼軒環球影業公司總裁錢重遠從業逾20年，曾製作《狼圖騰》、《最愛》、《小時代》等影視作品，他表示自己是《銀英傳》粉絲，很開心實現夢想。<br />\n日本網友熱烈討論此消息，大多既期待又怕受傷害，「抵抗獨裁的故事交給中國公司拍」；「這部作品根本沒什麼亞洲人的角色」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171102/1233398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171102%2F1233398&d=CknTApklNdW2AWKdhM4IHP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e0c273b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171102%2F1233398&h=fc13874b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171102/1233398</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171102/640_0b9e8e21afe018ecc35c70f738ac34cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171102%2F640_0b9e8e21afe018ecc35c70f738ac34cc.jpg&h=9a930c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾"},{"pid":"856ec6615ca1c137aa814f3a837f2ba6d1412b69","tid":455381,"uid":52358,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"搵楊利偉拍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ec8f7cf646125b86f41696053df34810927d4e","tid":455381,"uid":23635,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"有預感會有景